### Sequencer

"roxy/core/sequences/RoxySequence.lua"
"roxy/core/sequences/SequenceManager.lua"
"roxy/core/sequences/roxy_sequence.h"
"roxy/core/sequences/roxy_sequence.c"
"roxy/utilities/roxy_ease.h"
"roxy/utilities/roxy_ease.c"

Sequence functionality and flat easing functions in Roxy were adapted from Nic 
Magnier's Playdate Sequence library. However, RoxySequence has been 
extensively modified and expanded upon to fit the specific needs and design 
patterns of the Roxy Game Engine. These modifications include unique 
implementations, and performance enhancements that distinguish RoxySequence 
from the original library.

PlaydateSequence (https://github.com/NicMagnier/PlaydateSequence) is licensed 
